OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with a
OL,6,Fmixture of late sunny spells and
OL,7,Fvariable cloud this evening. Remaining
OL,8,Fdry overnight with occasional clear
OL,9,Fspells. Winds easing and turning
OL,10,Fchilly in any rural spots with some
OL,11,Fmist and fog patches.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FGenerally cloudier on Sunday,
OL,14,Fwith cloud thick enough for the odd
OL,15,Fspot of rain, but largely dry. Feeling
OL,16,Fwarmer in the sunny spells that
OL,17,Fdevelop.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
