OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells on Monday. Cloudier
OL,7,Ffrom Tuesday with a little rain at
OL,8,Ftimes towards the north and west.
OL,9,FTurning windier, especially by
OL,10,FWednesday. Remaining rather warm
OL,11,Fthroughout.
